## §2 Types from the OpenAPI spec

**Detected pattern**: {{TYPES_PATTERN}}

<!-- e.g.:
- Handwritten in src/api/types/ — one file per service, field names mirror spec exactly
- Generated by {codegen tool} from spec files
- Mix (legacy handwritten + generated for new specs)
-->

**Rules:**
- {{TYPES_RULES}}

<!-- Example:
- Request/response types match spec field names character-for-character. No "friendlier" renames.
- Nested structured shapes stay structured. Do not flatten `{coverImage: {present, required}}` into `{hasCover, hasRequiredCover}`.
- Enum values are identical to the spec's enum literals.
-->

